history.content:
<md>I'm looking to enroll on the waitlist for EECS 16B (I do not have a reserved seat), but the little checkbox that usually shows up to enroll on the waitlist in CalCentral seems to be missing entirely for EECS 16B (https://imgur.com/5YWHwOR). This is the only class where the waitlist checkbox is missing for me. Any suggestions/guidance for what to do would be greatly appreciated.

Edit: For some reason, when you click on the imgur link, there's an extra "%29" appended to it; delete those characters to properly view the image.</md>
